<script>\\n    (function(params) {\\n        var closeEl, closeBubbleEl, closeItemsEl, closeWrapEl, closeOverEl;\\n        var pixels = {\\n            ni: \\"https:\\/\\/rs.mail.ru\\/sb36635784.gif?\\",\\n            ab: \\"https:\\/\\/rs.mail.ru\\/sb36635789.gif?\\",\\n            sp: \\"https:\\/\\/rs.mail.ru\\/sb36635790.gif?\\",\\n            cv: \\"https:\\/\\/rs.mail.ru\\/sb36635791.gif?\\"\\n        };\\n        function stopE(e) {\\n            if (e) { e.preventDefault(); e.stopImmediatePropagation(); }\\n        }\\n        function addElemEvent(E, eventName, callback) {\\n            E.addEventListener ? E.addEventListener(eventName, callback, !1) : E.attachEvent && E.attachEvent(\\"on\\" + eventName, callback);\\n        }\\n        function removeElemEvent(E, eventName, callback) {\\n            E.removeEventListener ? E.removeEventListener(eventName, callback, !1) : E.detachEvent && E.detachEvent(\\"on\\" + eventName, callback);\\n        }\\n        function dispatchEvent(el, type) {\\n            var evt;\\n            if (typeof window.CustomEvent === 'function') {\\n                evt = new CustomEvent(type, {\\n                    bubbles: true\\n                });\\n            } else {\\n                evt = document.createEvent('CustomEvent');\\n                evt.initCustomEvent(type, true, false, null);\\n            }\\n            el.dispatchEvent(evt);\\n        }\\n        function sendPix(pix, params) {\\n            var img = document.createElement('img');\\n            img.src = pix || '';\\n            img.style.display = 'none';\\n            params.closeWrapEl.appendChild(img);\\n        }\\n        function getParentBannerItem(el) {\\n            var retval = null;\\n            var parentAttr = 'data-closewrap-container';\\n            var parentEl = el;\\n            while (parentEl) {\\n                if (parentEl === document.getElementsByTagName('body')[0]) {\\n                    retval = null;\\n                    break;\\n                } else if (parentEl.getAttribute(parentAttr)) {\\n                    retval = parentEl;\\n                    break;\\n                }\\n                parentEl = parentEl.parentElement;\\n            }\\n            return retval;\\n        }\\n        function getParentBannerSlot(el) {\\n            var slotClassName = 'mrg-tag';\\n            var slotEl = el;\\n            if (typeof el.closest === 'function') {\\n                return el.closest('.' + slotClassName);\\n            }\\n            while (slotEl !== null) {\\n                if (slotEl.className.indexOf(slotClassName) !== -1) {\\n                    return slotEl;\\n                }\\n                slotEl = slotEl.parentElement;\\n            }\\n            return null;\\n        }\\n        function closeAll(params) {\\n            params.closeWrapEl.className = params.closeWrapEl.className.replace(' _active', ' _hidden');\\n            removeElemEvent(params.closeEl, 'click', onCloseClick);\\n            removeElemEvent(params.closeOverEl, 'click', hideClose);\\n            for (var i = 0; i < params.closeItemsEl.length; i++) {\\n                removeElemEvent(params.closeItemsEl[i], 'click', onCloseReasonClick);\\n            }\\n        }\\n        function onCloseReasonClick(params, e) {\\n            stopE(e);\\n            var pix = pixels[e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-reason')];\\n            if (pix) { sendPix(pix, params); }\\n            sendPix(params.closeEl.getAttribute('data-closepix'), params);\\n            closeAll(params);\\n            \\/* dispatch close event to RbExt *\\/\\n            var parentBannerSlotItem = getParentBannerSlot(params.closeWrapEl);\\n            if (parentBannerSlotItem) {\\n                dispatchEvent(parentBannerSlotItem, 'mrg-close');\\n            }\\n        }\\n        function onCloseClick(params, e) {\\n            stopE(e);\\n            if (params.closeWrapEl.className.indexOf(' _active') === -1) { showClose(params); } else { hideClose(params); }\\n        }\\n        function hideClose(params, e) {\\n            stopE(e);\\n            params.closeWrapEl.className = params.closeWrapEl.className.replace(' _active', '');\\n            var parentBannerWrapItem = getParentBannerItem(params.closeWrapEl);\\n            parentBannerWrapItem.className = parentBannerWrapItem.className.replace(' _close-overlay', '');\\n        }\\n        function showClose(params) {\\n            params.closeWrapEl.className += ' _active';\\n            var parentBannerWrapItem = getParentBannerItem(params.closeWrapEl);\\n            parentBannerWrapItem.className += ' _close-overlay';\\n        }\\n        function init() {\\n            if (!params || !params.rootId || !document.querySelectorAll) return;\\n            var rootElem = document.getElementById(params.rootId);\\n            if (!rootElem) return;\\n            closeWrapEl = rootElem.querySelectorAll('.js-close-cross-wrap');\\n            if (!closeWrapEl || !closeWrapEl[0]) return;\\n            closeEl = rootElem.querySelectorAll('.js-close-cross');\\n            closeBubbleEl = rootElem.querySelectorAll('.js-close-cross-bubble');\\n            closeOverEl = rootElem.querySelectorAll('.js-close-overlay');\\n            for (var k = 0; k < closeEl.length; k++) {\\n                closeItemsEl = closeWrapEl[k].querySelectorAll('.js-close-reason');\\n                if (!closeEl || !closeBubbleEl || !closeOverEl || !closeWrapEl[k] || !closeEl[k] || !closeBubbleEl[k] || !closeOverEl[k]) return;\\n                addElemEvent(closeBubbleEl[k], 'click', function(e) {\\n                    e.stopImmediatePropagation();\\n                    e.preventDefault();\\n                });\\n                addElemEvent(closeEl[k], 'click', onCloseClick.bind(null, {\\n                    closeWrapEl:closeWrapEl[k],\\n                    closeEl:closeEl[k],\\n                    closeBubbleEl:closeBubbleEl[k],\\n                    closeOverEl:closeOverEl[k],\\n                    closeItemsEl:closeItemsEl\\n                }));\\n                addElemEvent(closeOverEl[k], 'click', hideClose.bind(null, {\\n                    closeWrapEl:closeWrapEl[k],\\n                    closeEl:closeEl[k],\\n                    closeBubbleEl:closeBubbleEl[k],\\n                    closeOverEl:closeOverEl[k],\\n                    closeItemsEl:closeItemsEl\\n                }));\\n                for (var i = 0; i < 			 <script type="text/javascript" >
			 try {
			     (function(global, name, url) {
			         url = url || '//r3.mail.ru/j/';
			         var yaads = global[name] || [];
			         global.yaads_rb_logs = global.yaads_rb_logs || {};
			         function get_charmap() {
			             var exceptions = [34, 35, 37, 47, 60, 62, 63, 75, 91, 92, 93, 94, 96, 107, 123, 124, 125];
			             var charmap = {
			                 46: 33, //. => !
			                 45: 36, //- => $
			                 32: 40 //  => (
			             }
			             var fbc = [38, 39, 43, 61, 126];
			             /*["&", "'", "+", "=", "~"] - some browsers uses percent-encoding for this symbols, but we stil can use it in charmap for any rare thing. NB! ~ (126) is used as field separator*/
			 
			             var not_avaliable = exceptions.concat(fbc);
			             for (var k in charmap) {
			                 not_avaliable.push(charmap[k]);
			             }
			 
			             var code = 33;
			 
			             function get_code() {
			                 while (code < 127 && not_avaliable.indexOf(code) >= 0) {
			                     code += 1;
			                 }
			                 return code++;
			             }
			 
			             var ranges = [
			                 [48, 58], // - digits
			                 [97, 123], // - latin
			                 [1072, 1104], // - russian
			                 [1105, 1106] // russian "—ë"
			             ];
			 
			             for (var i = 0; i < ranges.length; i++) {
			                 var s = ranges[i][0],
			                     f = ranges[i][1];
			                 while (s < f) {
			                     charmap[s] = get_code();
			                     if (!charmap[s]) throw new Error('can\'t encode character ' + String.fromCharCode(s) + '(' + s + ')');
			                     s++;
			                 }
			             }
			             return charmap;
			         }
			         function encodeStr(str, charmap) {
			             var unknown = 32;
			             var replacements = [
			                 [/\s/g, ' ']
			             ];
			             str = str.toLowerCase();
			             for (var i = 0; i < replacements.length; i++) {
			                 str = str.replace.apply(str, replacements[i]);
			             }
			             var coded = [];
			             for (var i = 0, l = str.length; i < l; i++) {
			                 var c = str.charCodeAt(i);
			                 c = charmap[c] ? charmap[c] : charmap[unknown];
			                 coded[i] = String.fromCharCode(c);
			             }
			             return coded.join('');
			         }
			         function getUrlLogItem(data) {
			             var charmap = get_charmap();
			             var title = data.assets.filter(function(ob) {
			                 return ob.title;
			             }).pop();
			             title = title && title.title && title.title.value || '';
			             var text = data.assets.filter(function(ob) {
			                 return ob.data && ob.ext && ob.ext.type === 2;
			             }).pop();
			             text = text && text.data && text.data.value || '';
			             var domain = data.assets.filter(function(ob) {
			                 return ob.data && ob.ext && ob.ext.type === 11;
			             }).pop();
			             domain = domain && domain.data.value || '';
			             if (!title || !text || !domain) {
			                 return '';
			             }
			             return [encodeStr(domain, charmap), encodeStr(title, charmap), encodeStr(text, charmap)].join(String.fromCharCode('126'));
			         }
			         function setLogs(data, newAdIds) {
			             var adItems = [];
			             for (var a = 0; a < data.adIds.length; a++) {
			                 if (newAdIds.indexOf(data.adIds[a]) !== -1) {
			                     adItems.push(data.bid[a]);
			                 }
			             }
			             var bound = (2083 - url.length);
			             var l = 0;
			             var ind = 0;
			             var ads = [];
			             while (ind < adItems.length && l < bound) {
			                 var adItem = adItems[ind];
			                 var itemData = adItem.adm.native;
			                 /*if (!!itemData.adType || adItems.length === 1) {*/
			                     // —É –µ–¥–∏–Ω—Å—Ç–≤–µ–Ω–Ω–æ–≥–æ –≤ –º–∞—Å—Å–∏–≤–µ –Ω–µ—Ç adType, –Ω–æ —É–∂–µ –æ—Ç—Å–µ—è–ª–∏ –≤—ã—à–µ –ø–æ adIds
			                     var str = getUrlLogItem(itemData);
			 
			                     l += str.length;
			                     if (l > bound) break;
			                     if (!!str) {
			                         ads.push(str);
			                     }
			                 /*}*/
			                 ind++;
			             }
			             // console.log(url + ads.join('/'));
			             new Image().src = url + ads.join('/');
			         }
			 
			         Object.defineProperty(window, 'yaads', {
			             get: function() { return yaads; },
			             set: function(newYaads) {
			                 if (newYaads.callSuccessCb) {
			                     var oldCS = newYaads.callSuccessCb;
			                     newYaads.callSuccessCb = function(t) {
			                         // console.log('Render data', t);
			                         var seatbidData = t.data.seatbid;
			                         var idInLogs = global.yaads_rb_logs.hasOwnProperty(t.id);
			                         var globalItemadIds = idInLogs ? global.yaads_rb_logs[t.id].adIds : [];
			                         var newAdsIds = [];
			                         var adIds = seatbidData[0].adIds;
			                         if (adIds && adIds.length) {
			                             for (var arrInd = 0; arrInd < adIds.length; arrInd++) {
			                                 if (globalItemadIds.indexOf(adIds[arrInd]) === -1) {
			                                     newAdsIds.push(adIds[arrInd]);
			                                 }
			                             }
			                         }
			 
			                         if (!!newAdsIds.length) {
			                             setLogs(seatbidData[0], newAdsIds);
			                             if (!idInLogs) {
			                                 global.yaads_rb_logs[t.id] = {};
			                             }
			                             global.yaads_rb_logs[t.id]['id'] = t.id;
			                             global.yaads_rb_logs[t.id]['adIds'] = globalItemadIds.concat(newAdsIds);
			                         }
			                         oldCS.call(newYaads, t);
			                     }
			                 }
			                 yaads = newYaads;
			                 // console.log('Try set yaads:', newYaads)
			             },
			             enumerable: true,
			             configurable: true
			         });
			     })(this, "yaads");
